Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:15.91,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}也會用盡想像力克服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.58,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}要是一不小心陷入僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.91,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}那時候便去隨機應變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:25.12,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}本應是一無所有的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:28.38,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}卻為此歡呼雀躍停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:30.68,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}這個世界將一定是
